See files in docs/ for more info.

For instructions on how to build ntop from source, see docs/BUILD-NTOP.txt (*nix) and docs/BUILD-MinGW.txt (Win32)

For instructions on hwo to run ntop the 1st time, see docs/1STRUN.txt.

Online information is at http://www.ntop.org, including archives of the ntop mailings lists.

Contributions of effort towards writing, rewriting and updating ntop's documentation would be heartily welcomed!

